功夫，围绕选优配强基层带头人这个关键下功夫；</p><p style="text-indent: 2em;clear: none;white-space: normal;"><strong>要抓出质量发挥作用，</strong>农村党建要聚焦富民强基，城市党建要聚焦治理创新，新兴领域党建要聚焦融合发展。</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="width: 20px;height: 20px;float: right;background-color: rgb(209, 19, 19);"></section><section style="clear: both;"></section></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.66640625" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/YVTZQsOL5lMAlX5TbqKmtwPjQQQHjqSOKP8rLZUSkwBFTRnS0wr3icsrsoU8vl6sHjO1HGNAqBOEQHEkkntM3Mg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" style=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br  /></p><section><section class="V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;margin-bottom: 11px;width: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(209, 19, 19);border-left: 1px solid rgb(209, 19, 19);height: 8px;transform-origin: center bottom 0px;transform: skew(-30deg);border-top-color: rgb(209, 19, 19);border-bottom-color: rgb(209, 19, 19);"></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 5px;"><p><strong>周乃翔强调</strong></p></section><section style="margin-right: 4px;margin-bottom: 4px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(209, 19, 19);border-left: 1px solid rgb(209, 19, 19);height: 8px;transform-origin: center bottom 0px;transform: skew(-30deg);border-top-color: rgb(209, 19, 19);border-bottom-color: rgb(209, 19, 19);"></section></section><section style="height: 12px;margin-top: -12px;border-top: 1px solid rgb(209, 19, 19);"></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em;margin-b